des: "Avocado gives these pops a great creaminess without a lot of unhealthy fats. Taste and adjust sweetness and saltiness to taste before freezing."
ins: Blend avocado, coconut milk, agave nectar, lime juice, vanilla extract, and salt in a blender until smooth, about 1 minute. Pour mixture into ice pop molds and freeze until solid, 2 to 3 hours.
